data.description: REDUCED & SELLER OFFERING $20,000 AT CLOSING FOR YOU TO USE FOR UPDATING OR INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN OR CLOSING COST!! Welcome to your new spacious pool home, nestled on a cul-de-sac in Glenwood with no HOA. Offering a generous split floor plan, impact windows/garage/sliders, 2010 tile roof, new Electrical panels, owned solar panels, updated sprinkler system, well-maintained AC, home water filtration system & more! Start your day with coffee or alfresco dining on the oversized, screened-in patio, overlooking pool & updated stamped concrete deck. The backyard features a fully fenced, large, lush yard with endless possibilities for outside living or expanding home. Easy access to major highways, hospitals, excellent shopping & dining. Welcome to your dream home!
